    "naming_note": "Renamed 2026-07-10 (migration d5f7a9c1e3b5) — the table name IS the Amazon report type. The old name `rpt_fba_reimbursements` still resolves as a read-only compat VIEW; prefer `rpt_get_fba_reimbursements_data` in new queries.",
